<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201122/ea09c085c08c429c8452dcd9d679b0d6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>【欧尚领导致欢迎词】</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201122/a7aa3cb0a4114d93a45d223c1f3d5fe6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>【店总经理全方位车型讲解】</p>
